Take Sun Rong to the infirmary now.

303
00:16:21,720 --> 00:16:24,270
Split the heaven door
with one strike of my Master.

304
00:16:24,970 --> 00:16:25,770
Sword Master, congratulations on

305
00:16:26,220 --> 00:16:29,350
